name: Vol 1., Ch.2: Rough Times Ahead
description:
The first couple of days were a bit rough for Tiara. Most of the girls at school already knew each other, so she feels like an outsider. “Beware of the boys- stay away from them!” was the advice her mother gave, but it seems as if the boys were not interested in her.

A month after, however, things start to change. One day, as she enjoyed her sushi roll alone in the cafeteria, two cute girls approached, with big smiles on their face. “Hi Tiara! Can we have lunch with you?” Minutes after they are all laughing and sharing friendly gestures at the table, telling stories of their past.
